title: M.r.zeidabadi

content: Calmoairphoenix company is a new startup in the aerospace industry. The main goal of this company is to create airplanes which are suitable (safe, easy to fly, easy to maintenance, and economic) for everyone. The products of this company include 2-seater to 10-seater airplanes.The seed-sale stage of this company is active.For more information please visit calmoairphoenix website: https://calmoairphoenix.com/
